measurements.description: Seventy-eight striking, slightly cupped flowers and one bud on five up to 21.5-cm inflorescences; sepals cream overlaid deep burgundy apical two-thirds, lateral sepal falcate; petals cream blotched burgundy basally, apical two-thirds deep burgundy; lip trilobed, cream, sidelobes heavily overlaid and striped burgundy, midlobe blotched dark burgundy, callis light yellow; column cream; substance medium; texture glossy.
